Rule 2     sections -> section sections
Rule 3     sections -> section
Rule 4     section -> TEXTSEC : INT section_body
Rule 5     section -> DATASEC : INT section_body
Rule 6     section -> TEXTLABELS { label_defs }
Rule 7     section -> DATALABELS { label_defs }
Rule 8     label_defs -> ID : INT label_defs
Rule 9     label_defs -> ID : INT
Rule 10    section_body -> word section_body
Rule 11    section_body -> word
Rule 12    word -> INT
Rule 13    word -> REF

Terminals, with rules where they appear

:                    : 4 5 8 9
DATALABELS           : 7
DATASEC              : 5
ID                   : 8 9
INT                  : 4 5 8 9 12
REF                  : 13
TEXTLABELS           : 6
TEXTSEC              : 4
error                : 
{                    : 6 7
}                    : 6 7

Nonterminals, with rules where they appear

file                 : 0
label_defs           : 6 7 8
section              : 2 3
section_body         : 4 5 10
sections             : 1 2
word                 : 10 11

